'''阿貝爾370'''是位於[[鯨魚座|鯨魚座]]，距離[[地球|地球]]40億[[光年|光年]]遠的[[星系團|星系團]]，在它的核心有數百個星系。這個星系團登錄在[[喬治·阿貝爾|喬治·阿貝爾]]的星表中，並且是目錄中距離最遠的星系團。

== 重力透鏡 ==
阿貝爾370看起來有數個光弧，事實上這些是[[重力透鏡|重力透鏡]]對更遙遠天體的[[蜃景|蜃景]]造成的<ref>''New York Times'', [http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=940DE6DC1E3BF93BA25753C1A96E948260 "SCIENCE WATCH; Mirages in the Sky May Not Be So Rare"] {{Wayback|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=940DE6DC1E3BF93BA25753C1A96E948260 |date=20200229184044 }} Tuesday, October 18, 1988</ref>。

在2002年，天文學家使用這個透鏡的效應發現了距離地球128億光年遠的星系[[HCM-6A|HCM-6A]]，是當時所知最遙遠的星系<ref>BBC News, [http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/low/sci/tech/1871043.stm "Far away stars light early cosmos"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/low/sci/tech/1871043.stm |date=20040309204054 }} Thursday, 14 March, 2002, 11:38 GMT</ref>。

在2009年，對阿貝爾370的研究發現一個背景中的星系群被星系團中的透鏡扭曲成像是一條龍的弧形，因此就被NASA的科學家暱稱為'''龍(The Dragon)'''<ref>Astronomy Now, [http://www.astronomynow.com/news/n0909/09hubble/ "Refurbished Hubble gets off to a flying start"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.astronomynow.com/news/n0909/09hubble/ |date=20160303233453 }} 09-09-09 (accessed 2009-11-07)</ref><ref>New York Times, [http://www.nytimes.com/slideshow/2009/09/09/science/0909HUBBLE_3.html "The Universe, in High Definition"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/slideshow/2009/09/09/science/0909HUBBLE_3.html |date=20170807152104 }} 09/09/09 (accessed 2009-11-07)</ref>。頭部是由一個螺旋星系組成<ref>''New Scientist'', [http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn17765 "Upgraded Hubble telescope spies cosmic 'dragon' "] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn17765 |date=20150321201530 }} 09.09.09 (accessed 2009-11-07)</ref>，另一個螺旋星系構成了尾部。其他幾個星系構成了身體，而它們都有所重疊<ref>National Geographic, [http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2009/09/photogalleries/new-hubble-camera-first-pictures/photo6.html "NEW HUBBLE PICTURES: First Shots From Upgraded Orbiter"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2009/09/photogalleries/new-hubble-camera-first-pictures/photo6.html |date=20160811100050 }} Saturday, November 7, 2009 (accessed 2009-11-07)</ref>。這些星系的距離大約在50億光年<ref>''Times of India'', [https://web.archive.org/web/20090913224515/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/news/science/After-repairs-new-space-images-from-Hubble-unveiled/articleshow/4994169.cms "After repairs, new space images from Hubble unveiled"] 10 September 2009 (accessed 2009-11-07) </ref>。

